In a message dated 4/22/03 12:14:16 AM Central Daylight Time, 
airly2002@... writes:


> "Sure..."replied th femme with a wide smile"What have I do?"
> 
> 

She turned, "First... follow me. I'm sure we can spar & do some target 
practice." inwardly she would need it for the next time she met up with 
Rodimus. She wanted to have a piece of him, to battle him personally, to 
damage him but let him suffer until Hydras terminated him. 

She glanced back at Blackstorm & smirked. At least, the first torture for 
Rodimus would be very sweet. Turning Blackstorm into a cold & vicious killer, 
with no trace of whatever she once was. 

"Perceptor informs me that you need a little practice as well. Though I don't 
call it practice.. but preparation. You are a fembot. A Predacon or 
Decepticon fembot at that." she started as they moved to find a sparring 
area, hopefully they had a room large enough. "Decepticon fembots were, & 
still are, vicious... shadowy.... emotionless... precise... lethal... 
assasins & warriors." She stopped & turned to Blackstorm. "It's time to count 
yourself as one of those few who could be worthy in the optics of Megatron." 
She deep femme voice resounded in confidence.


--part1_e4.37ae5fc6.2bd6bfe0_boundary
